header: Test vectors of type AeadTest test authenticated encryption with
additional data. The test vectors are intended for testing both

notes.CounterWrap: AES-EAX reduces the counter value modulo 2**128. This test vector was constructed for testing the wrapping of the counter value.
notes.SmallIv: AES-EAX allows arbitrary sizes for the nonce. This test vector uses an IV smaller than 12 bytes.

tests.comment: no counter overflow, but the 64 most significant bits are set.
bits 32-64 and 96-128 of counter are set
lower bits of initial counter are 2^63-1
lower 64 bits of initial counter are 2^63-4
